{"tid":94732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【代表D咩】中國財赤超標創新高 比預算超出6千多億","createTime":"2017-01-25T12:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T06:38:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fbe2e85958d5d8c90eeb2ebeba354cc2d1c79e5f","tid":94732,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"中國財政部公布 2016 年全國財政收支數據，在一般公共預算支出方面達到 18.78 萬多億，增長了 6.4%，導致全年財政赤字有 2 萬 8 千 1 百億。 <br />\n<br />\n對比去年 3 月全國人大通過的財政預算案，財政赤字比預算超出了 6 千多億。 <br />\n<br />\n在財政部公布的主要支出項目中，債務利息支出高達 4,991 億元，增幅超過四成，而各項民生支出的增幅，只保持在 10% 至 20% 左右。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/619412508250821/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F619412508250821%2F&d=uKxilzV8Tp9rAPgAIDIpuXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=ca56fc1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/619412508250821/</a>"},{"pid":"07b4651d463a03f717a70493d2fead4a8ae9bb84","tid":94732,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:25:16.000Z","msg":"代表高官又加提成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6b7ac7ef129ac2748754ec94275f3e82183c8f","tid":94732,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:27:09.000Z","msg":"太陽照常升起"},{"pid":"a784abc014880c55897a2fabe349b18473e6d5b8","tid":94732,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"支那狗做生做死<br />\n狗官一下拎去外國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeec8842578b2174391b38b52b6c29bf300275e6","tid":94732,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"唔怪得之香港物業成交量多左咁多"},{"pid":"6a669873aed34af22cb0bc7c1bed41d43e16e6d7","tid":94732,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T13:54:52.000Z","msg":"當然代表支那又成為最大羸家 仲可以係乜?"},{"pid":"64e87fe09